title: 100 Blocks 2007-2011
name: 100 Blocks 2007-2011
description: This layer represents the Urban Strategies attempt to map the one hundred most dangerous blocks in Oakland. We used Oakland Police Department reports of homicides and assaults from 2007 - 2011 within census 2010 blocks and out a certain buffer distance. The coordinate system is EPSG: 4326 or GCS WGS 1984.
